data.description: just wide of short leg. Nips back in from a short of length and cramps Buttler for room, he squeezes an inside edge and the ball goes wide of Rana at short leg. Buttler off the mark with a brace

data.title: Jofra Archer to Buttler, no run
data.description: greeated with a pacy short ball. He even walks up and has a word with Buttler. Well-directed bouncer, Buttler sways out of the line and allows it to sail over him. This is exciting stuff..

data.title: Jofra Archer to Shubman Gill, out Bowled!! Cleaned up! That's Archer at his best. Even Gill goes uhhh as he walks back.  full delivery around off
data.description: Gill is drawn into the forward push and he is a tad late on the shot, the ball also swings in to beat the inside edge and crash into off-stump. Gill was left surprised with the movement even as he missed the shot. B2$

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Rahul Tewatia, 1 run
data.description: shortish delivery, Tewatia mistimes the pull to long-on and keeps strike

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: yorker around off stump, Sai swings and gets an inside edge that rolls to short fine leg

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: it's back to back boundaries off Sandeep now after he's kept it so quiet. Again the wide line theory, Sai was ready for it. This time was a bit easier as it wasn't that wide and he nailed the lofted drive over cover

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, SIX
data.description: hey youuu! That's unbelievable. How did he hit that for six? This is wide of off again, it's length and Sai opened his wrists and sliced it so hard. It looked like sweeper was going to swallow that but even a jump couldn't make that possible. Such was the power and timing behind the shot

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Rahul Tewatia, 1 run
data.description: pace off, Tewatia taps it to backward point

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Rutherford, out Caught by Samson!! It's the wide line again to Rutherford that works wonders. PBKS outsmarted him here in GT's first game of the season with that strategy. Sandeep continues with that baton. This was length and very wide of off stump. Rutherford tried to reach out and slap
data.description: would have been a wide had he left it but it's an outside edge through to Sanju.

data.title: Jofra Archer to Rahul Tewatia, no run
data.description: the fast bumper! Tewatia lets it pass

data.title: Jofra Archer to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: pace off short ball, Sai swings and gets a top edge, doesn't have the legs to carry to fine leg

data.title: Jofra Archer to Rahul Tewatia, 1 run
data.description: yorker, Tewatia taps it to point

data.title: Jofra Archer to Rahul Tewatia, wide
data.description: fired leg side. Tewatia will feel he missed out on a freebie. He is so good with that pick up flick/slog-sweep

data.title: Jofra Archer to Rahul Tewatia, SIX
data.description: pace is a boon but it can be a bane as well! Jofra Archer has actually surprised the batter with a full toss and found a top edge, but because of the high pace it's flown all the way over the keeper's head for six. Tewatia wanted to hit fine leg, but it went the other way

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: expensive over, 18 runs. Deshpande releases all the pressure that was built by Archer. He attempts a slower ball and offers width, Sudharsan delays his square drive and cracks it through point. There was a sweeper but he had no chance of stopping that

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Buttler, 1 run
data.description: fullish delivery, Buttler eases it towards mid-off and scampers across easily

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: on a length and close to off, Sudharsan guides it towards backward point and quickly crosses over

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: shot! Not quite off the middle but the ball still races away. Good length ball around off, Sudharsan drives on the rise and sends it straight back past Deshpande. It came more off the inner half but still beat Archer comfortably to the fence

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, wide
data.description: full and strays down leg, Sudharsan misses the clip and Samson dives across to glove the ball

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, SIX
data.description: this is smart batting. Sudharsan moves across his stumps, gets under the back of a length deliver and laps it over fine leg. The pace of Deshpande takes it all the way..

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: short of length and cramping the batter, Sudharsan hops and drops it into the off-side

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, wide
data.description: starts with a  down leg, Sudharsan misses the glance and a scoring opportunity

data.title: Theekshana to Rutherford, 1 run
data.description: oh he wanted a slog over square leg now! Fullish and down leg, Rutherford went really hard, ball seemed to have gone off the leg, no off the bat in fact

data.title: Theekshana to Rutherford, SIX
data.description: oh ho ho! Sherfane Rutherford you beast! Theekshana just missed the yorker, Rutherford got under that and absolutely smashed it high over long-on. First ball and he left nothing in the tank

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, out Stumped!! Well bowled and well kept. SRK stepping out to muscle the ball. Theekshana smartly fired this wide of off stump
data.description: SRK had nowhere to hide and this time Samson wasn't blinded. Had his eyes on the ball, stayed low and calmly collected to effect an easy stumping. Deserved wicket for Theekshana but SRK can be proud of what he's done. He's ensured GT didn't get bogged down.

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 2 wides
data.description: great save from Samson again! Another leg-side yorker, Samson dives and saves the boundary down leg

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 2 runs
data.description: another yorker. Smashed down the ground. Riyan cuts it off with a fast roll at long-off

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, 1 run
data.description: gun yorker, SRK works it to deep mid-wicket

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 2 wides
data.description: oh almost outsmarted him there but this is a very, very tough chance for Samson. Firstly Theekshana yorked Sai with a leg-side ball as the batter advanced. The batter would have obviously blinded the keeper and Samson did well to get his hand on it. You can't expect thosd to be stumped. And Sai nearly ran himself out at the non-striker's end as they try to steal an extra run. Sandeep has a shy from short fine leg but misses

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: slot, thank you very much says Sai and lofts the drive hard over cover off the front foot

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: full pitcher on leg, Sudharsan makes room and drives to long-on

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 2 runs
data.description: knuckle ball angled in, Sudharsan flicks it backward of square and picks up a brace

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Buttler, 1 run
data.description: shimmies down and almost yorks himself, digs it out to long-on

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: slower ball that curls in, Sudharsan waits and punches it wide of long-on

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Buttler, 1 run
data.description: strays onto the pads, Buttler clips it to deep square leg

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Buttler, wide
data.description: short ball right at Buttler and he takes it on, swings across for the hook but the ball sails over him. Called a  for height

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Buttler, no run
data.description: good length ball outside off, Buttler shuffles down and across, turns it straight to mid-wicket

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Buttler, no run
data.description: full and slanted outside off, Buttler reaches and mistimes the drive to mid-off

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: good length ball around off, Sudharsan plays it with soft hands to the off-side and Buttler crosses over

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, 2 runs
data.description: slanting in from back of a length, Sudharsan tucks it backward of square and scampers back for the second

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, SIX
data.description: whoa! Sudharsan charges down and Farooqi saw him coming, he goes for the short ball and Sudharsan adjusts quickly to play the ramp, he uses the pace on the ball and sends it sailing over third man

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Buttler, 1 run
data.description: full toss and it swings in, Buttler clips it to deep square leg

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Buttler, no run
data.description: angled outside off, Buttler goes chasing with feet laden to the crease and almost nicks off

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, no run
data.description: lovely ball from Theekshana though. A proper yorker but stunned SRK. He swung and missed, ball sneaked under the bat and went to the keeper. The batter was overbalancing. Even Samson was done in by that ball and he couldn't collect. Ball hit the pad and disturbed the stumps but SRK just had his back foot grounded to escape the stumps

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, FOUR
data.description: ah this is class batting! He knew Theekshana was going to hide it wide of off, he was ready with an open bat face and reached out with the long levers of his to slice this past backward point

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, FOUR
data.description: it's an edge this time but it's in the gap! Full and outside off stump, SRK throws his bat at it as he has the licence. Thick edge makes backward point and short third man mere spectators

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, SIX
data.description: he's belted that out of sight! The boundary size hardly matters for this big hitter. Hit me short ball, SRK was quick to rock back and muscle this pull high and handsome way over mid-wicket

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: bit of width, Sai mistimes the slap to long-off

data.title: Theekshana to Shahrukh Khan, 1 run
data.description: flatter delivery, SRK works it to deep mid-wicket

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Shahrukh Khan, 1 run
data.description: low full toss outside off, Shahrukh drives to sweeper cover and retains strike

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Shahrukh Khan, wide
data.description: very full and outside off, Shahrukh fails to squeeze it out. They ponder about a review for the  and decide against it

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Shahrukh Khan, SIX
data.description: fabulous shot! Deshpande misses the yorker and is dispatched into the crowd. Overpitched outside off, Shahrukh creams the lofted cover drive over extra cover and sends it sailing all the way..

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Shahrukh Khan, wide
data.description: too short and too high, Shahrukh shimmies down and aborts from the shot as he knew that was way over

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Shahrukh Khan, no run
data.description: speared into the blockhole, Shahrukh digs it to the left of Deshpande

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: very full and around leg, Sudharsan ekes out an inside edge onto the pad and the ball rolls to square leg

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: charges down and attempts to loft through the line, beaten on the outside edge

data.title: Tushar Deshpande to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: Deshpande continues to leak runs.. Slower short ball outside off, Sudharsan had ample time to jump up and play the upper cut to the vacant deep backward point region, one bounce and over the ropes

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: fullish delivery, Sudharsan leans forward and drives to sweeper cover

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Shahrukh Khan, 1 run
data.description: short and banged into the surface, Shahrukh attempts the ramp and gets it off the outer half to third man

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Shahrukh Khan, no run
data.description: once more pace off and Shahrukh does not pick, swings to the leg-stump and does not connect

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Shahrukh Khan, no run
data.description: slower short of length delivery, Shahrukh is through the pull early and misses it completely

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Shahrukh Khan, FOUR
data.description: back to back fours. Wrong line from Farooqi - strays onto the pads, Shahrukh backs away and clips it backward of square, Sandeep dives near short fine but can't reach the ball

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Shahrukh Khan, FOUR
data.description: streaky! Back of a length delivery, Shahrukh is cramped for space but still looks to pull, gets an under-edge and the ball did not miss the stumps by much

data.title: Jofra Archer to Sai Sudharsan, 2 runs
data.description: short of length delivery, Sudharsan pulls it wide of mid-on and collectd a couple

data.title: Jofra Archer to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: back of a length outside off, Sudharsan crouches low and attempts the ramp, fails to connect

data.title: Jofra Archer to Shahrukh Khan, byes
data.description: 1 run, short ball around leg, Shahrukh takes it on but the bounce is too much for him, misses the hook and Samson has to leap to his right to parry it away, saved a few

data.title: Jofra Archer to Shahrukh Khan, no run
data.description: off-pace short of length delivery, Shahrukh is through the pull early and the ball goes on the bounce to Samson

data.title: Jofra Archer to Shahrukh Khan, 2 runs
data.description: full delivery at the stumps, Shahrukh is rooted to the crease and closes the bat face trying to turn it into the leg-side, gets a leading edge and the ball lands in front of sweeper

data.title: Jofra Archer to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: direct hit and Sudharsan was gone. Full pitcher close to off, Sudharsan drives firmly to mid-off and sets off on a suicidal run, Sandeep swoops down and has a shy at the non-striker's end, misses and Sudharsan survives. He put in the dive but was still short as the ball passed the stumps

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, out Lbw!! Theekshana is pumped. He has broken this partnership. This looked real close to the naked eye but the onfield umpire was not convinced. Buttler misjudges the length here. He thinks it is short and goes for the pull
data.description: but good length ball skids across and strikes him on the back leg, the impact was in front of middle and leg, ball-tracking showed it to be smashing into leg-stump.

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, no run
data.description: low full toss around off, Buttler drives it to the left of Theekshana and he sticks his hand out to make the stop

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: third fifty for the season. Just a raise of the bat and punch of gloves with Buttler. He struggled against Archer but saw that phase through and has cashed in. He reaches the landmark with a nudge into the leg-side

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: goes quicker and perishes. drifts in and ends up right in the swinging arc, Sudharsan kneels down and nails the slog sweep wide of deep mid-wicket

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: slows up the off-break, Sudharsan drives it back to Theekshana

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, 1 run
data.description: attacks the stumps, Buttler stays back and knocks it to long-on

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, FOUR
data.description: Buttler has found his rhythm. Full pitcher and right in the slot, still had to be put away and Buttler smashes it straight back over Theekshana, couple of bounces and over the rope

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, 2 runs
data.description: once more fires it outside off, Buttler drives wide of sweeper and collects a couple

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, FOUR
data.description: flatter delivery and skids across, Buttler hangs back and drives it in front of square, beats cover inside the ring and also gives Jaiswal no chance getting across from long-off

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: sliding in from round the wicket, Sudharsan rocks back and pulls to deep mid-wicket

data.title: Theekshana to Buttler, 1 run
data.description: fraction short close to off, Buttler chops it wide of point

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: short of length around off, Sudharsan punches it to sweeper cover

data.title: Theekshana to Sai Sudharsan, wide
data.description: starts with a dart down leg, Sudharsan tries to help it along the way but does not connect

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: that's more like it. Good length ball in the channel and this time Farooqi gets it to swing away, Sudharsan is rooted to the crease and has a tentative poke, beaten on the outside edge

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, 2 runs
data.description: good length ball close to off, Sudharsan opens the bat face and guides it through the vacant backward point region, scampers back easily for the second

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, FOUR
data.description: width, no swing and dispatched. Short and outside off, Sudharsan pounces on it, he opens the bat face and carves it square on the off-side. No need to run for that..

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: another inswinger from a fullish length this time, Sudharsan drives off the inner half and picks out mid-on

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: swings in from good length, Sudharsan hangs back and turns it gently to mid-wicket

data.title: Fazalhaq Farooqi to Shubman Gill, 1 run
data.description: on a length and angled across, Gill ekes out an inside edge onto the pad and the ball rolls to the off-side

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: to the T again! Wide yorker with backward point and deep point in place, Sai could only drill the drive to the latter

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, no run
data.description: excellent! Wide yorker, Sai squeezes and finds point

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Shahrukh Khan, 1 run
data.description: another attempt for a big heave but SRK drags it to wide long-on. These two TN boys have now added 50 runs in this stand

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: wide yorker attempt, Sai belts the drive but finds deep point

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Shahrukh Khan, 1 run
data.description: wants the muscle the pull but finds deep mid-wicket

data.title: Sandeep Sharma to Sai Sudharsan, 1 run
data.description: width outside off stump, Sai slices to deep backward point
